araday, a descendant of famous physicist Sir Michael Faraday. Moving on to the barrel display area your guide will describe the various stages of the maturation process. You will also learn about our other products - Merlyn Cream Liqueur, Brecon Five Vodka, Brecon Special Reserve Gin and Brecon Botanicals Gin. Your tour will end in our tasting bar where you are entitled to taste two of our products, OR, take a miniature bottle away with you.&nbsp; You may then browse the gift shop at your leisure.","url":"\/businesses\/2801"}},{"id":"ty_newydd_country_house","lat":51.7509468,"lon":-3.5280779,"enhanced":true,"type":"accommodation","popup":{"title":"Ty Newydd Country Hotel","image":"","text":"","url":"\/businesses\/2852"}}];
